Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=6}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.21,0:00:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...{*}no{*chan}. Hey, come on, listen!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.66,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! Look at what I found!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oasis Festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.70,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This was back when the oasis\nwas still the size of a lake.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for you. As a memento.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just precious?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.22,0:00:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a miracle happened\nand Abydos started booming agai—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,ED,Miracles don't exist, {*}Yume{*Senpai}. {Probably fine, but also consider "Miracles aren't real"? --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,ED,They're only in fairy tales. {"They only happen in fairy tales" or something might be better. --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Face reality.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.20,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would {\i1}anyone{\i0} ever come\nto the middle of the desert?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even entertaining the idea is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.10,0:00:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is go on and on\nabout useless stuff like miracles.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the president of the Abydos student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of responsibilities,\nso start acting like it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.97,0:02:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiroko{**-chan}, got a second to talk?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About yesterday, well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I was also being too pushy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.20,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're just worried about li'l ol' me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.28,0:03:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,ED,The Abydos Task Force\nisn't complete without all five of us. {Consider "Forclosure Task Force" instead of "Abydos[...]". Makes more sense as the shorthand imo. Or you could use the full name like in JP, but that might become stilted in English. --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, you're so sweet.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.26,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're hiding from us,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I really did luck out,\ngoing to the same school as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.40,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how the land Abydos owned\nwas transferred to a third party?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We looked deeper into it,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.96,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it turns out that the land is currently\nowned by "Kaiser Construction".
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the Kaiser Corporation after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The only property we own\nis this building and its surroundings.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.88,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything else, the main building buried underneath\nthe sand, the miles of wasteland surrounding it, {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.51,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the infrastructure and land in the city,\nare owned by them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually can't trade land owned by a school district.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.26,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This deal originated from the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? What were they thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.38,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they have just handed over\nAbydos's land to those creeps?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.64,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Each school's district is the property of that school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply common sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.56,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so caught up repaying our debt\nthat we never even suspected this could happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.75,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. If only I had realized this sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This all happened long before anyone enro—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you part of the student council, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\nyou were the vice president, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.38,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, it was just me and the president.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Just two of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.11,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. By then, the student population\nhad already dropped into the double digits.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.14,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff had all up and left,\nand actual classes were a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the student council room\nwas just being treated like a fancy storage room.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The president was the biggest klutz at school,\nwith hardly a thought in her head.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I was the new kid with the bad attitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire situation was one big mess.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? How is that even a student council?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.57,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing more than a couple of dum-dums\ndoing dumb things together at the end of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.87,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, those were the days.\nAll we did was loiter around.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.37,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2690,4483,\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HFDFDFD&)}Just two clueless idiots,\nstuck in their own little world.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't blame yourself for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened in the past,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.60,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but what I {\i1}do{\i0} know is that without you,\nthe Task Force wouldn't be what it is today.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always lazing about.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You never give a straight answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's only the start of your problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.89,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're always the first to step up when we need you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I respect you. {Clearly this should be translated as "I'm confessing to you" smh homophobic fansubbers --ML}{confess your crimes, shiroko --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's this coming from, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just drop a line like that out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.38,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,why did the student council sell their land\nto the Kaiser Corporation in the first place?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.79,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably did it to pay off their debt at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just my guess.\nI wasn't there when it happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.88,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they were trying their best for the school,\nbut the debts just kept piling up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe so, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.82,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's unlikely all the land\nclaimed by the desert had much value.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.98,0:06:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have paid back the interest,\nbut they couldn't have reduced the principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.52,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result, they were forced\nto sell more and more land.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the game was rigged from the start! {is that a NV reference --ML}{The bear and the bull --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First, they make a loan that could never be paid off.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.74,0:07:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, they pressure the school to sell their land\nin order to pay even a portion of the debt back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.12,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the end of it, the entire school district\nwill have fallen into the Kaiser Corporation's hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This was probably their plan from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.97,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they lent Abydos money in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.20,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap may have been set\nfar earlier than we realised.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.38,0:07:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Decades ago, even.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.82,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,ED,What? That means Kaiser\nplayed them like a damn fiddle! {As much as I really do appreciate this reference, I feel like perhaps its a little too blatant? --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they fell for this scam! {you're one to talk --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Serika.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the perpetrators\nare to blame here, not the victims.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People become desperate\nwhen backed into a corner.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll do anything, even if they know\nit'll only make things worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all this is, Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The school's debt,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos's current situation,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.86,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and these new discoveries we just made...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.28,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all the pieces are starting to fall into place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.95,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Abydos student council disbanded,\nthey lost their ability to buy more land.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.16,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to take over this final piece of land,\nthey hired the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.02,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the Kaiser Corporation\nwas never after the money?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.17,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Their true goal was the land itself all along?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that begs the question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they want land\nthat's buried under the desert?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.52,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What could they possibly stand to gain\nfrom taking over Abydos?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the desert,\nright after we fought Gehenna...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The abandoned desert in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.67,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3970,4179,\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HFDFDFD&)}The Kaiser Corporation is plotting something there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? How does the Head Prefect\nof Gehenna know about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I mean, there was a lot going on!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like sensitive information, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, but you should have just told us!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.18,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.94,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Now we know that Kaiser\nwas the one buying out the land.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they're plotting something, we should act.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}'s right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.75,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The answers to all of our questions\nmust be hidden in the Abydos Desert.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.12,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,ED,Yes. {I would probably go with "Right" instead of "yes" here --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Abydos Desert!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have to hoof it from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.25,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have you collapsing on us out here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this part to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, now this is a blast from the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here before?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A few times for student council work.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit further and you'll find\na great oasis waiting for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An oasis?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.14,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a dried-up oasis, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.64,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be where they'd hold\nthe Abydos Oasis Festival every year.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oasis Festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very well known within Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently it attracted a ton of people!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.91,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be such a big event,\nit even attracted students from other schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Big enough to attract them\nall the way to the desert?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.59,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, from what I heard this place\nused to be much more hospitable.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Hoshino{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure your lead was any good?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the oasis where they\nused to hold the Oasis Festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a large structure ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be what Hina was talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.14,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, everyone. We don't know what's out there. {no shit ayane --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay cautious while you investigate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's swarming with guards.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck even is this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.39,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This appears to be yet another one\nof the Kaiser Corporation's subsidiaries.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,PMC...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it means?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,PMC stands for "Private Military Company".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.61,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, they're mercenaries.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nothing like the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are professional soldiers.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruders spotted!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into position!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, this could get messy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prefects were already bad enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless! Retreat!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who we have here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard we had some intruders,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.29,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wasn't expecting to find\nAbydos students at my front door.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that student council president\nGematria was interested in.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, their vice president, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect you to know at least that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.02,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,TLC/QC,I'm one of the directors of the Kaiser Corporation. {### TLC: gamecheck pls. iirc there was a board of directors, but I could be wrong}{I also forget how their corporate structure is --ik} {he is listed as a director in the wiki, double checked --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} him!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the guy behind all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.17,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who swindled\nthe student council out of their land?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd advise you watch your tone, young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.47,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're currently trespassing on the property\nof our company, Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.36,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to test my patience.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the topic at hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned the land Abydos used to own.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.74,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we did in fact buy that land.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a completely legitimate transaction.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We even have the records to prove it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.98,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you must be wondering why we\nwould purchase {such a massive sandpit :^)}this massive, barren wasteland.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,ED,Allow me to happily explain. {I can't exactly put my finger on why, but something about "happily explain" feels wrong to me. --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.58,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for a treasure\nsaid to be buried somewhere in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You really expect us to believe that crap?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you have an army?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.26,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were planning on taking Abydos\nby force. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.85,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They are bodyguards to protect us from\npotential disturbances during our treasure hunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not here for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could deal with you whenever I wanted.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone call? Now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some very bad news.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.18,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.73,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The interest rate starting next month\nhas increased to three thousand percent!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merely dogs,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm the one holding your leash.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we could pay that interest rate!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just\ngive up and leave your school?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw from school,\ntransfer elsewhere, doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.09,0:15:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This debt is the school's responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.82,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you, as students, carry that burden?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way we could just leave!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.39,0:15:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! We're not abandoning Abydos!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos is our school. It's our home!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what will it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other options?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. Time to go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in arguing with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just toying with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A wise choice, Miss Vice President. {SASUGA} {askcully this should be "As expected of the Vice President of Abydos"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a smart cookie.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.88,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,ED,{\t(6110,6220,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I'm shocked someone so smart was willing\nto follow that brainless idiot of a president. {Consider putting the newline after "to" --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.97,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. I am eager to see those monthly repayments.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.46,0:16:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again, cherished customers,\nfor choosing Kaiser Loan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God! What the hell was that crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.68,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He said they were looking for a treasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.80,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos collected survey reports long ago\nwhile searching for oil and other resources.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The desert is empty. There's nothing of value there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find out what they're up to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you want to go back there?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.62,0:17:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take time to prepare,\nI think I can infiltrate that base.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.83,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to think about\nhow to deal with the debt first.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The debt's too big. We can no longer\npay it back by playing fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Shiroko{**-senpai} here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.71,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose the school, it's all over!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.30,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to be picky!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Think this through, Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.13,0:17:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do this, it'll be no different from\nwhen we robbed the bank!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.07,0:18:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really say we saved Abydos\nif we used money we stole from elsewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let you become criminals!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.86,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,QC,Come on, everyone.\nLet's all calm down a bit. {### tempted to use chillax here frfr}{take a chill pill, simmer down, stop - hammer time --ik} {light i agree with the chillax --rapid}{### petzku you heard rapid. Let me do it let me do it let me do it}{calm down y'all - sika}{I feel like chillax wouldn't really fit the tone here ngl --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see steam coming out your ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.98,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.98,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't want things to get so heated.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We all understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.38,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go cool off\nand meet up again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, president's orders! Go rest!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Hoshino{*Senpai}'s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.78,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.42,0:19:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entertaining useless ideas like miracles\nand happy endings, huh? {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. That's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when did you and\nmy little Shiroko{**-chan} become so close?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.65,0:19:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I could practically see you reading each other's minds.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.13,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to keep a closer eye on you, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit awkward to say face to face.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.34,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if we walk and talk, {*}Teach{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.82,0:20:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,High school is supposed to be fun, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda sad if it's all covered in sand, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you like this school, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.27,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that before the desert moved in,\nAbydos was known for its size and influence. {i feel like this is ever so slightly off, it feels like shes more saying "Abydos was knows for being such a big and strong force," and  less so for noting why people were attracted to it --rapid}{### So more like "military prowess"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.35,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was before my time.\nI never got to see it like that myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a complete mess from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.43,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't one thing the school actually did right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.50,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,QC,But despite all that,\nyou still love this school, right?{I kinda want there to be emphasis on "this is THE (singular) school you (came to) love" but this is fine}{### maybe petz has ideas for this}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.44,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I enrolled, the main building\nwas already hidden deep underneath the sand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.85,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The school kept relocating as the desert expanded,\nand this annex is where it ended up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.67,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know, if I hadn't come here,\nI wouldn't have met everyone in the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess I do like this school after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.87,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a load off my chest!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,ED,If I told everyone this,\nthey'd all just worry, y'know? {I feel like this should be "told everyone about this", assuming she's referring to what is discussed offscreen after "the truth is" --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.98,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know I can't go keeping secrets\nfrom my adorable little clubmates forever either.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.31,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like they need more on their plate, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you for telling me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.99,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll understand\nwhat you're going through.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.73,0:21:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The road ahead is long, but as long as\nwe stick together, we can make it to the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe a miracle will happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.95,0:21:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can make one happen\nif we're all together.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.23,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough serious talk for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.42,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{=7}See you tomorrow!

